message.content:
1. Patient-reported HRQoL and disease-related symptoms were evaluated.
2. The evaluation used the FACT-Ovarian (FACT-O) questionnaire.
3. The FACT-O questionnaire was completed at baseline.
4. The FACT-O questionnaire was completed every 28 days until progression.
5. The evaluation also used the FACT/NCCN Ovarian Symptom Index (FOSI).
6. The evaluation also used the Trial Outcome Index (TOI).

messages.content:
